{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "青龙对残暴的艾缪尔大失所望后，\\n将王子视为新的主人，并与其缔结契约。\\n这时帝国的骑士哈尔出现了。\\n一行人得知皇帝正向绯龙发起进攻，\\n决定向绯龙栖息的火山进发。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "呼……呼……\\n青龙，已经够了吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "没有理由再和你战斗下去了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "喂喂喂！身为我的龙，\\n怎么能输给这种家伙？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "喂，站起来！快给我站起来！\\n你还能打吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "呜……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "住手吧，艾缪尔！\\n不要再让龙受伤了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "闭嘴！别把我当笨蛋！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "哥哥也是……姐姐也是……你也是！\\n总是这样！用高高在上的语气讲话！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "我可是很厉害的！\\n只要认真起来，我就是最强的！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "所以……龙！快站起来！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "哇！\\n居然敢对我放箭，太无礼了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "给我出来！我要教训教训你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不许动！\\n如果你再对龙动手，\\n我就用箭射穿你的脑袋。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "你这混蛋！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "曾挑战我的森隐族啊。\\n为何要保护袭击了你故乡的我？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "你手下留情了吧？\\n因此我才得以存活。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "这只是还你一个人情。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "我并不后悔\\n贸然挑战过你。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "为了想要守护的东西，\\n我会拼上性命，挺起胸膛！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "尤蒂尔也一样。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "比起名誉，我们更想守护尊严和梦想。\\n所以我们站得比谁都直！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "你又如何，青龙！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "侍奉不成器的主人，尊严惨遭践踏……\\n你想守护的到底是什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "你是在问我吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "没错，青龙！\\n身为至高无上的龙，\\n你所期望的究竟是什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "我所期望、想要守护的是……\\n我的宝物——美丽的水之地。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "艾缪尔向我发过誓，\\n会用金钱和权力\\n保护那片珍宝般的土地。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "龙！那种土地根本无所谓！\\n快点打倒他们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "无所谓！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "艾缪尔，你向我保证会保护的土地，\\n居然说无所谓！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "没错，一文不值！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "什么清澈的水，什么泥沼，\\n这些都无所谓！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "只要有契约在，\\n你就是我的奴仆！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "快点，去战斗！去战斗啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "你竟然……\\n龙和王族的契约\\n是真心诚意、神圣而崇高的存在……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "而你却……\\n如此轻易地改变主意……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "现在你明白了吧，青龙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "艾缪尔\\n是不值得缔结契约的人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "你的力量\\n不该用来帮助那种人\\n实现他的野心。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "可是……那样的话，我的愿望就……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "因为登上陆地，\\n远离了深爱的那片沧海的守护者……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "原来如此，青龙……\\n那片海才是你的故乡……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我明白……\\n人、龙、森隐族……\\n大家热爱故乡的心情都是一样的。\\n既然如此……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "青龙啊，\\n我发誓会替艾缪尔保护你的宝物！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "替他……保护？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "开、开开、开什么玩笑，你这混蛋！\\n胡说八道什么呢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "那种事怎么可能做得到！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "我会的。我在这里起誓，你的宝物……\\n那美丽的水之地，由我来保护！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "那环绕全身的光芒……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "莫非你才是……\\n真正……继承了龙之血的人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "既然这样，那我也舍命问你。\\n现在的契约是真是假。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "赌上生死的“断绝龙环”！\\n哪怕散为魔力，也死而无憾。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "“断绝龙环”！难道你……\\n喂！住手！不经我允许就擅自……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "呃！呜……\\n哈啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "诶诶诶，这家伙竟然\\n自己打破了契约之环。你会死的哦！？\\n给我去死啊去死去死去死去死！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "哈啊，哈啊……意识……还在……\\n成功了吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "青龙！你还好吗？\\n来吧，就是现在！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "好！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "继承了龙之血的王子啊，\\n再度向你确认。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "你为何而战斗？\\n为何还想获得龙之力？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不论多少次我都会回答。\\n我想要，能保护想要守护之人的力量。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "没能保护重要的人，\\n让我体会到被夺走的悔恨……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "所以，我想得到更强的力量！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "心中没有迷茫，眼神没有虚假。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青龙",
            "context": "那光芒所展示的王的潜质……\\n以我的名义为你祝福！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "墨丘利",
            "context": "我乃墨丘利。\\n激流之主，波涛之王。\\n此刻起将成为你的母亲海！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "这、这这、这不是真的！契约石！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "竟然擅自抛弃我，\\n跟别人缔结契约！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "墨丘利",
            "context": "并不是擅自……\\n这份契约之所以能被认可，\\n是因为你当初的誓言有假。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "你这叛徒！\\n我一辈子都不会原谅你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "墨丘利",
            "context": "与龙的契约是把双刃剑。\\n你终有一天会明白。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "墨丘利",
            "context": "器量不够的人是无法承受的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_1036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "哈！哈！哈！\\n居然连龙都被夺走了，\\n可怜的艾缪尔大人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "哈尔！你来得太晚了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0069",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100017_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "艾缪尔",
            "context": "赶快打倒这些家伙，\\n夺回我的龙！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0070",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "更让我震惊的是，\\n优秀的尤蒂尔大人！",
