            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0074",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "哈尔",
            "context": "王国已经\\n被皇帝亚罗拉斯大人毁灭，\\n而且龙也正被赶尽杀绝！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0075",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "父王，不……\\n那个男人，竟然把龙！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0076",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "哇！是、是地震？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0077",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不，不是！山顶上在冒烟……\\n阿德拉火山喷发了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_02_08_0078",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "那座山是绯龙栖息的……\\n莫非皇帝的目标是……",
